Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠻勇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者是在找死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(1075,575)\blur1\bord2.5}白銀的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准將 如何處理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻回收指揮機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓一讓 讓一讓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們哪部份的?不要出長城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是獨立第八部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獨立第八部隊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要前去營救昔日長官 左文字雨京大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多包涵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是很感人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧他說的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說那種話不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今這狀況只能靠氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八部隊請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止左文字雨京 這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混小子居然打紅眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宰了他也得搶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟上獨立第八部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓奪回長城的英雄白白送死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救出左文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿嘴謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這狀況 我要利用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人不是撤退了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友軍也開始攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒你們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色殲滅者 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除我和你們之外都是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員各自為戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 是銀殲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別大意 時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 希爾菲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手在這呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀殲 已注意到我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜 要是沒機會吃飯還請多包涵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這個沒門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃意麵 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為母則強?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經為母了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按時宗的節奏 該進白刃戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要相信他的單純 看你的了帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意麵 意麵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗君第一招會{\rsymbol}…{\r}衝頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在 勞倫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勞倫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長 看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再補一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勞倫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 我們也撐不久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我老實聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頂住啊 勞倫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意麵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米{\rsymbol}·{\r}哈茲福特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辨識密碼 0612 0530
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認啟動認證
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉寫 吉米{\rsymbol}·{\r}哈茲福特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和上次看的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 來看我 看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著我 銀色殲滅者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了時宗 盡情衝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米小姐 奈美惠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍曹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪 銀色殲滅者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是銀色殲滅者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:06:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫里希特霍芬來 就是為了這一刻?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概不論戰局如何 我都想成全那傢伙完成自己的本願
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在這見證 直到您的最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即刻起 誘敵深入 開始進一步包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不是找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪 左文字先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特殊工兵部隊聯絡 即將與指揮機接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真諷刺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越是指揮大部隊 你的機體越像木頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪 銀色殲滅者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誘捕器 激活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小子{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你小子想尋死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准將 大事不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後方有大部隊接近 推測是鎮壓部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泉大佐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:08:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 又要被剝離出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不交給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Link系統 白銀的意志 是麗華心願的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它以這個形式{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 這個戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麗華在最後的實驗前對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rsymbol2}「{\r}看著我{\rsymbol2}」{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒等我去面對 她就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以白銀的意志到最後{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到最後一刻都要由我見證
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從銀色殲滅者上下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 是屬於你和我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信它去戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能只是看著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得伸手抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色殲滅者 你 是屬於我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是個大蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你我們才活到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許戰場真的很醜惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 多虧有你我才能融入部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才覺得自己找到了歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你卻要做這種事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做的事只是自私
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了這種事 少拿出姐姐的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少特麼提我姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字隊長 到此結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白銀的意志 所有U-Link系統即刻死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與我們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我遵守了諾言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願意 看著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選擇了自盡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中央發來指令 要求一時休戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備真周到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下令撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的宏圖{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一度點燃的火 可沒那麼容易熄滅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,願隨您左右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何滿腦都是這想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別痛苦 特別孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺自己要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡面有我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喲 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的部隊被泉打敗 潰不成軍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈爾米亞也撤軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和泉的計劃成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說你的真正目的 又另在他處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果我們 只是被迫看你和南條麗華的殉情大戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對想尋死的你 這可能算是慈悲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一琢磨我都不想開槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但公私要分明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行李裝好沒?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重啟銀色殲滅者時 我體會到好多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能接受吉米的思緒 我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對一個人原來是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越川說開卡車從這邊繞一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 我和軍隊都沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是你今後怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯貝爾尼斯倒閉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說沒就沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 反正沒了銀色殲滅者我也沒工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 是誰啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勝呂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說啥來啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是哈茲福特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 事後處理脫不開身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間不長但辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離職金給你匯過去 記得查收一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 離職金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,匯款搞錯了三位數 嘛無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 副產物也出了不少 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得想想下一個公司的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人情我還了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼續盯著韋爾德利貝爾特的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白銀的意志是沒了 但系統構想目前還留著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字在系統中 好像見到了麗華
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說看到就當看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是他心中白銀的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元帥的處分是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,處分?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字是奪回長城的功臣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有人把死去的海燕准將看做英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有授勳但也不會定罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 我就是討厭軍隊這點才不幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 元帥的戰爭還會繼續咯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還得讓左文字走一條更艱苦的路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是他想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不準{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正當元帥的 可能會是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還這麼見外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 到王都前都順路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧我說吧 你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果新工作決定去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先去柯貝爾尼斯競爭對手們那邊看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿經驗豐富當賣點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊整備兵隨時歡迎你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是最後的保險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人離心不離也很重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊對了 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是席加
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路線確認 沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員 準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾個月後 阿蘭達斯與因戈爾米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,締結了停戰協定和互不侵犯條約
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互換聯絡官 規定互相開放情報
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很明顯 這只不過是表面上的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭達斯的聯絡官已經抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來阿蘭達斯軍中也不乏有想法的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知是用做棄子 還是做獅子身中蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論如何 我都會利用到骨髓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭達斯軍 聯絡官閣下帶到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請他進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.34,0:21:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭達斯軍少佐 左文字雨京
